quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  4,87,"Alla, rewetee…óo e goonga alaa si wanaa KaŇčko, ma O Moo…ďitoy on fow √Ďalnde Darnga nde sikke alaa e mun ; fii no O Yo…ďitira on golle mon. Alla ∆Āur…óo Alla goongude e yeewtere."
  4,88,"Ko wa…ói on onon gom…óim…ďe …ďen feddeeji …ói…ói e fii …ďee naafiqii…ďe : fedde goo hino wi'a waree …ďe sabu keeferaaku ma…ď…ďe, fedde goo wi'a acciree…ďe sabu gom…ói…óal ma…ď…ďe ngal ! On haanaano luutondirde fii ma…ď…ďe. Alla Ruttirii…ďe e keeferaaku sabu golle ma…ď…ďe …óen. E on faala fewnude on mo Alla Majjini laawol goonga ngol ?! Kala on mo Alla Majjini, a he…ďaŇčtaa mo fewnoowo."
  4,89,"Naafiqi en no yeloo sinno on yeddayno kon ko Jippinaa e moo…óon wano …ďe yeddiri non, laato…óon fotoo…ďe e ngol yeddugol. Wata on jogito immorde e ma…ď…ďe yi…ó…ďe haa …ďe fera e laawol Alla ngol immo- immorde galle sirku faade ka leydi lislaamu fii felliŇčtingol liimanaaku ma…ď…ďe. Si …ďe …óuurnike gaay …óum, nanngee …ďe waron …ďe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ďe. Wata on jogito e ma…ď…ďe gi…óo, wanaa kadi ko wallindiron e ay…ďe moo…óon."
  4,90,"Si wanaa …ďen …ďe hino jokkoo e ma…ď…ďe faade yim…ďe …ďe ahodi…óon tertagol hare, maa…óum …ďe arii on hara …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen hino faa…óani ha…ďugol on, maa ha…ďugol yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen. Si Alla Haajuno, O Warayno …ďe e moo…óon, …ďe ha…ďa on. Wata on ha…ďu …ďe maa dahon. Si …ďe pottitike on, …ďe ha…ďaali on, …ďe arii e mon fii mo∆ī∆īintingol, haray dey Alla Wa…óanaali on e dow ma…ď…ďe laawol ha…ďugol …ďe maa dahugol …ďe."
  4,91,"Onon gom…óim…ďe …ďen, arma nde tawoton fedde goo e naafiqi en no fe√Ī√Īinana on gom…óinal fii no …ďe faabinora on, …ďe fe√Ī√Īinana yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen keeferaaku ngun tuma …ďe ruttii e ma…ď…ďe fii no …ďen kadi faabora …ďe. Tuma kala non nde …ďe ruttitaa e yeddugol Alla ngol sirkana Mo, …ďe ugginite e mun ko tii…ói. ∆Āen non si ha…óitaaki ha…ďugol on, …ďe ari e mun fii mo∆ī∆īiŇčtingol, …ďe ha…ói juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen meemugol on ; haray nanngee …ďe waron …ďe nokku kala ka taw…óon …ďe. ∆Āen siforii…ďe …óii sifaaji, Men Wa…óanii on e nannugol …ďe ngol wara hujja …ďanngu…óo ; sabu pewje ma…ď…ďe …ďon…óe …óen."